{"tid":1289051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅范椒芬：有到連登討論區了解市民意見","createTime":"2019-07-06T02:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T02:47:09.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9da87a7274ea768be3cfcb171752660b43531af8","tid":1289051,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1466899_1_L_20190706095736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1466899_1_L_20190706095736.jpg&h=b53dd2a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員羅范椒芬表示，有到連登討論區看市民意見，明白很多人對政府有更高期望，想政府走得更前，但特首要平衡社會不同訴求，她認為政府已覺得無路可退，大家再迫政府，作用亦未必大，不如一起向前看。<br />\n<br />\n羅范椒芬在本台節目表示，現時一些野貓式的抗議行動沒有領袖或代表，如何接觸不同聲音是不易處理的課題。她說，年長的人士仍然會從社會經濟問題看青年訴求，但青年是很重視價值觀，講求理想及追求自由與法治，當局從房屋問題著手都不是對焦的做法，要對青年保證政府會極力捍衛法治與自由。<br />\n<br />\n羅范椒芬又認為，不能直接說青年輕生的問題是政府責任，同樣不能說通識教育令青年上街。她說，社交媒體影響比通識教育更大，如果沒有通識科教導學生批判、查看不同資料，可能會有更多學生上街。"},{"pid":"23f1ce8aac117947201060cb8c1c203970e412e8","tid":1289051,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:19:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466899-20190706.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466899-20190706.htm&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=b1b73196\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466899-20190706.htm&h=ed3f9f76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466899-20190706.htm</a>"},{"pid":"527ae038a35a70fb429c90e9e65d779048ccfed1","tid":1289051,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f071f0497767c8042318a752c68a198d12159d7f","tid":1289051,"uid":166974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":